<p>Imagine that you publish an ad but people that are interested in contacting another department within your company but not your add. You can create a custom field for this specific purpose. If you don’t know how, you can follow this guide.
For that you can create a custom field. <em>If you don’t know how, you can follow <a href="//docs.yclas.com/how-to-create-custom-fields">this guide</a>.</em></p>

<p>This custom field needs to be called <strong>contactemail</strong>. If that field exists emails will be sent to that address instead of the user’s email address.</p>

